description: What the Truck is bringing street food to Grand Rapids to show the masses that steamed hotdogs shouldn't be your only sidewalk food option.We're changing the Grand Rapids culinary landscape one street at a time. We try to source everything locally, If we're not able to grow it ourself or get it from Ingraberg Farms of Rockford. Everything is always made to order, from scratch. It's an unwavering principle we started at the Winchester (the mothership) and continues to our food truck.
name: What the Truck
